trans-unit.source: Contains the typical parameters for the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 包含 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> 演算法的一般參數。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the counter for the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 指定 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> 演算法的計數器。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the <see langword="G" /> parameter for the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 為 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> 演算法指定 <see langword="G" /> 參數。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the <see langword="J" /> parameter for the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 為 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> 演算法指定 <see langword="J" /> 參數。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the <see langword="P" /> parameter for the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 為 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> 演算法指定 <see langword="P" /> 參數。

trans-unit.source: `P` must be a prime number between 64 and 128 bytes long.
trans-unit.target: `P` 必須是介於 64 與 128 位元組長的質數。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the <see langword="Q" /> parameter for the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 為 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> 演算法指定 <see langword="Q" /> 參數。

trans-unit.source: `Q` must be a 160-bit prime factor of `P` - 1.
trans-unit.target: `Q` 必須是 160 位元主要因數`P`-1。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the seed for the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 指定 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> 演算法的種子。

trans-unit.source: The seed is the base number used for the generation of pseudo-random numbers.
trans-unit.target: 種子是使用虛擬亂數產生的基底編號。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the <see langword="X" /> parameter for the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 為 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> 演算法指定 <see langword="X" /> 參數。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the <see langword="Y" /> parameter for the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 為 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.DSA" /> 演算法指定 <see langword="Y" /> 參數。
